---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="International Business Advisory | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management delivers cross-border transaction advisory, company formation, global mobility, and compliance services across the EU, GCC, Asia, and Latin America."
>
<main>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__bg" id="hero-bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=1800&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">International Business Advisory · UAE Headquartered · Global Reach</span>
      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Empowering Innovation —<br>Quietly, across every border</h1>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">ARM Management advises international companies, investment funds, family offices, and high-net-worth individuals on cross-border transactions, company formation, global mobility, and compliance — across the EU, GCC, Asia, and Latin America.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <a href="/contact"  class="btn-primary">Speak With a Senior Advisor →</a>
        <a href="/services" class="btn-secondary">Explore Our Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__scroll"><span>Scroll</span><div class="hero__scroll-line"></div></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust bar -->
  <div class="trust-bar">
    <div class="trust-bar__inner">
      <div class="trust-stat"><span class="trust-stat__number">40+</span><span class="trust-stat__label">Jurisdictions Covered</span></div>
      <div class="trust-stat"><span class="trust-stat__number">15+</span><span class="trust-stat__label">Years Senior Advisory Experience</span></div>
      <div class="trust-stat"><span class="trust-stat__number">24/7</span><span class="trust-stat__label">Direct Advisor Access</span></div>
      <div class="trust-stat"><span class="trust-stat__number">100%</span><span class="trust-stat__label">Enquiry Confidentiality</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ARM Verify banner -->
  <section class="verify-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="verify-banner__inner">
        <div class="verify-banner__left">
          <div class="verify-banner__tag">ARM Verify — New</div>
          <h2 class="verify-banner__title">Verify Any Entity <span>Instantly</span></h2>
          <p class="verify-banner__sub">Real-time KYC <span>·</span> Sanctions Screening <span>·</span> UBO Mapping</p>
        </div>
        <div class="verify-banner__right">
          <a href="https://verify.arm-management.com" class="verify-banner__cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9c1.86 0 3.59.57 5.03 1.53"/></svg>
            Verify an Entity →
          </a>
          <div class="verify-banner__pills">
            <span class="verify-banner__pill">OFAC · UN · EU · UK HMT</span>
            <span class="verify-banner__pill">35+ Jurisdictions</span>
            <span class="verify-banner__pill">From $0.50</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Our Practice Areas</span>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Six Disciplines.<br>One Relationship.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal reveal-delay-2"></div>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="max-width:680px;margin-bottom:0;font-size:17px;color:#2C3240;line-height:1.8">ARM Management was built to answer a specific frustration: that international businesses operating across borders must manage five different firms with no single advisor who understands the full picture.</p>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:52px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="card__number">01</div>
          <h3>Cross-Border Transaction Advisory</h3>
          <p>Private investment, M&amp;A, acquisition support, and deal structuring across 40+ jurisdictions. Advisory-first. Success-aligned.</p>
          <a href="/services/transaction-advisory" class="btn-secondary">Explore →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="card__number">02</div>
          <h3>International Company Formation</h3>
          <p>Incorporate in the EU, GCC, Asia, or Latin America. Legal entity selection, VAT/EORI registration, director services — fully coordinated.</p>
          <a href="/services/company-formation" class="btn-secondary">Explore →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="card__number">03</div>
          <h3>Accounting, Tax &amp; Monthly Compliance</h3>
          <p>Monthly bookkeeping, VAT returns, corporate tax filings, and annual accounts across multiple countries — one ARM contact coordinates everything.</p>
          <a href="/services/accounting-tax" class="btn-secondary">Explore →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="card__number">04</div>
          <h3>Payroll &amp; HR Advisory</h3>
          <p>Strategic advisory on global payroll structure, HR compliance, international assignment planning, and multi-country workforce strategy.</p>
          <a href="/services/payroll-hr" class="btn-secondary">Explore →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="card__number">05</div>
          <h3>Global Mobility &amp; Residence Permits</h3>
          <p>UAE Golden Visa, EU Golden Visa, investor permits, company-sponsored residency, and family applications — managed end-to-end.</p>
          <a href="/services/global-mobility" class="btn-secondary">Explore →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="card__number">06</div>
          <h3>Crypto &amp; Web3 Advisory</h3>
          <p>VARA licensing, MiCA compliance, token structuring, DAO legal frameworks, and corporate setup across the world's leading crypto jurisdictions.</p>
          <a href="/services/crypto-web3" class="btn-secondary">Explore →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The ARM Standard -->
  <section class="section section--navy" style="position:relative;overflow:hidden">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486325212027-8081e485255e?w=1600&q=70&auto=format&fit=crop');background-size:cover;background-position:center;opacity:0.08"></div>
    <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">The ARM Standard</span>
      <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="color:#F7F3EC;max-width:720px">We are not the largest advisory firm.<br>We are the most committed one.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal reveal-delay-2"></div>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.78);max-width:680px;margin-bottom:52px">ARM Management was built on a principle we have never compromised: that clients deserve an advisor who is genuinely accountable for outcomes — not just for process.</p>
      <div class="grid-2" style="max-width:1000px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1.5px solid #B8960C;padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F7F3EC;margin-bottom:12px">Honest Assessment Before Commitment</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.62);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We evaluate every mandate and tell you directly what is realistic. We have declined engagements where we could not deliver what the client needed.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1.5px solid #B8960C;padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F7F3EC;margin-bottom:12px">Senior Advisors. Always.</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.62);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">The advisor you speak with in the first conversation is the person managing your engagement. No handoffs. No junior associates.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="border-top:1.5px solid #B8960C;padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F7F3EC;margin-bottom:12px">We Find the Alternative</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.62);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">We have never closed an engagement without providing at least one viable path forward. When the primary route is blocked, we identify the next solution.</p></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="border-top:1.5px solid #B8960C;padding-top:20px"><h4 style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F7F3EC;margin-bottom:12px">Available Around the Clock</h4><p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.62);font-size:15px;line-height:1.75">Cross-border business does not operate in one time zone. Neither do we. Active ARM clients have direct access to their advisor at any hour.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <section class="quote-section">
    <blockquote class="reveal">"The most valuable thing an international advisor can offer is not a network, and it is not a process. It is the courage to tell you the truth about what is possible — and the expertise to find a better way when the obvious path fails."</blockquote>
    <cite class="reveal reveal-delay-1">— ARM Management</cite>
  </section>

  <!-- Regions -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="reveal" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:52px">Four Regions. Forty Jurisdictions.<br>One Point of Contact.</h2>
      <div class="grid-4 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <a href="/regions/european-union" class="region-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1467269204594-9661b134dd2b?w=800&q=70&auto=format&fit=crop');background-size:cover;background-position:center">
          <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(13,27,42,.5),rgba(13,27,42,.85))"></div>
          <div style="position:relative;z-index:1"><h3>European Union</h3><p>All 27 EU member states plus UK and Switzerland. Company formation, VAT/EORI, accounting, payroll advisory, and EU Golden Visa programmes.</p><span class="arrow">Explore Region →</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/regions/gcc-middle-east" class="region-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=800&q=70&auto=format&fit=crop');background-size:cover;background-position:center">
          <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(13,27,42,.5),rgba(13,27,42,.85))"></div>
          <div style="position:relative;z-index:1"><h3>GCC &amp; Middle East</h3><p>ARM's home market. UAE mainland, free zones, DIFC and ADGM. Saudi Arabia (Riyadh office), Qatar, Bahrain. UAE Golden Visa. VARA crypto licensing.</p><span class="arrow">Explore Region →</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/regions/asia-pacific" class="region-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1525625293386-3f8f99389edd?w=800&q=70&auto=format&fit=crop');background-size:cover;background-position:center">
          <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(13,27,42,.5),rgba(13,27,42,.85))"></div>
          <div style="position:relative;z-index:1"><h3>Asia Pacific</h3><p>Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, India, Vietnam, Thailand, Indonesia, Japan. Market entry, incorporation, and accounting coordination.</p><span class="arrow">Explore Region →</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="/regions/latin-america" class="region-tile" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483729558449-99ef09a8c325?w=800&q=70&auto=format&fit=crop');background-size:cover;background-position:center">
          <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(13,27,42,.5),rgba(13,27,42,.85))"></div>
          <div style="position:relative;z-index:1"><h3>Latin America</h3><p>Mexico, Colombia, Brazil, Chile, Panama, Uruguay. Cross-border advisory, company formation, and regulatory navigation.</p><span class="arrow">Explore Region →</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Ready to Structure Your Next Move?</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Every ARM engagement begins with a confidential conversation. No obligation. No generic advice. A senior advisor will assess your situation honestly and tell you exactly what is achievable — and at what cost.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@arm-management.com" class="btn-secondary">info@arm-management.com</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<style>
  .card__number { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(184,150,12,.18); margin-bottom: 16px; }
</style>

<script>
  const bg = document.getElementById('hero-bg');
  if (bg) {
    setTimeout(() => bg.classList.add('loaded'), 100);
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => { bg.style.transform = `scale(1) translateY(${window.scrollY * 0.15}px)`; }, { passive: true });
  }
</script>
</Base>
